{"pageProps":{"currentData":{"ID":833333,"author":"1","author_nickname":"wpuser","author_display_name":"Chuckie Chang","author_url":"https://matrixflip.com/api","author_username":"wpuser","author_avatar":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/?s=96&d=mm&r=g","categories":[25],"categories_output":[{"ID":25,"slug":"%e7%94%9f%e6%b4%bb%e7%90%90%e7%a2%8e","name":"生活琐碎","term_taxonomy_id":25,"term_group":0,"taxonomy":"category","description":"","parent":0,"count":25}],"tags":[108,110,111],"tags_output":[{"ID":108,"slug":"jeep","name":"jeep","term_taxonomy_id":108,"term_group":0,"taxonomy":"post_tag","description":"","parent":0,"count":2},{"ID":110,"slug":"%e5%a4%a7%e8%87%aa%e7%84%b6","name":"大自然","term_taxonomy_id":110,"term_group":0,"taxonomy":"post_tag","description":"","parent":0,"count":1},{"ID":111,"slug":"%e8%87%aa%e9%a9%be%e6%b8%b8","name":"自驾游","term_taxonomy_id":111,"term_group":0,"taxonomy":"post_tag","description":"","parent":0,"count":1}],"thumbnail":[],"thumbnail_mini":[],"thumbnail_retina":[],"thumbnail_full":[],"date_day":"19","date_month":"02","date_month_e":"February","date_year":"2021","date_weekday":"Friday","title":"抓住当下，享受自然「 JEEP mini小房车行游记」","excerpt":"有时候单纯工作时很无聊的，要抽很多时间去做一些没有做过的事，比如探索大自然，极限运动，探险等等，它能让你忘记那些所谓的喧嚣繁杂，享受属于自己的时间。","content":"<p>有时候单纯工作时很无聊的，要抽很多时间去做一些没有做过的事，比如探索大自然，极限运动，探险等等，它能让你忘记那些所谓的喧嚣繁杂，享受属于自己的时间。</p>\n<p>我的小指可以说并不是日常代步工具，而是陪我去外面玩的伙伴。虽然不能硬派越野，但经常经过乡村乡道甚至山路中走走烂路也是不成问题的。户外就要考虑很多问题，脱困，睡觉，电源，休闲等等，所以我对它来了一些小小的改装，让它变成我的mini房车。其它它还是素车，并没有对大件进行过拆卸和更换（除了轮毂轮胎），去五金店买很多不锈钢配件，定制一些配件，以便能够将车内有限的空间和功能进行组装。</p>\n<p>好了，上图啦。</p>\n<h3>第一关: 全尺寸备胎问题</h3>\n<p>1.首先的定做了备胎架，加了锁，换上以前轮毂的全尺寸备胎到车顶（我喜欢在车顶，我的车顶就是放东西的，萝卜各有所爱，自己的车自己怎么喜欢怎么来，你不喜欢可以用原来车里的备胎），原来的胎就拿回家放着，位置空出来放了一些工具，比如车衣，充气泵和工具等。另外，我一个人可以举起备胎，车顶完全不是问题，虽然还是有点重，掌握技巧完全没问题。</p>\n<p><img src=\"/static-remote/files/183fb05b0033f8bbd38f8353-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsfbbfbbdfjpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>↑↑↑↑↑↑↑↑↑↑ 备胎用了普通的at100 ↑↑↑↑↑↑↑↑↑↑</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"/static-remote/files/d9cdf3a13d755cda9d9ce51f-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsdcdfadcdadcefjpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"/static-remote/files/05a6541c7ea56e6a354b582e-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsaceaeabejpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"/static-remote/files/4dd42a007c63c54195721fb0-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsddaccfbjpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"/static-remote/files/f1e9891a9db84e0b70e9d690-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsfeadbebedjpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>↑↑↑↑↑↑↑↑↑↑ 这是原来的备胎，拿回家放着 ↑↑↑↑↑↑↑↑↑↑</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"/static-remote/files/b6e9ee04f2e4fa257ff381d3-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsbeeefefaffdjpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>↑↑↑↑↑↑↑↑↑↑ 原来备胎位置 ↑↑↑↑↑↑↑↑↑↑</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3>第二关: 储物拓展</h3>\n<p>2.买了拓展板，以便让后备箱能空出来，可以睡觉，拓展板用的是帕杰罗和牧马人的。</p>\n<p><img src=\"/static-remote/files/d4942dc261ee204ef40bb223-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsddceeefbbjpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>下面的拓展板是经过处理的，取消了斜边，方便非原配车型组装:</p>\n<p><img src=\"/static-remote/files/387b9d1bf31932119d5937f6-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsbdbfdfjpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3>第三关: 金属连接件</h3>\n<p>3.五金店购买合适的工具，我这里主要用到u型夹，D型扣等,以便从侧边完成和拉手的组合，将拓展板挂上去。</p>\n<p><img src=\"/static-remote/files/d026d5c4bf33a36c004f81a4-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsddcbfacfajpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>↑↑↑↑↑↑↑↑↑↑上面是不同类型的卡扣，可以根据自己的需要，自己配置 ↑↑↑↑↑↑↑↑↑↑</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"/static-remote/files/f8fc045c180e88c4ef397cae-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsffccecefcaejpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"/static-remote/files/124a73cddcdbdc0903bb7b4d-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsacddcdbdcbbbdjpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"/static-remote/files/c2b1fed85cb73d644dcf5bb6-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadscbfedcbddcfbbjpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3>第四关: 车内休憩空间</h3>\n<p>4.只好把一些户外用品合理固定到拓展板上，后备箱放倒后中间位置空出来就可以睡觉了。车里侧窗和后窗都有定制窗帘，方便遮隐私，啊哈哈哈。车里有220v逆变器和水龙头的水箱，方便户外用水和用电（电脑或者一些小功率电器）</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3>第五关: 其它工具摆放</h3>\n<p>5.最后来个外观全貌，那根很长的不是鱼竿。</p>\n<p><img src=\"/static-remote/files/875bdedfeae3f27c9e827fb3-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsbdedfeaefcefbjpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"/static-remote/files/72cc3d061d8cef4015ffa008-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccddcefffajpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>↑↑↑↑↑↑↑↑↑↑ 来个全貌吧 ↑↑↑↑↑↑↑↑↑↑</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"/static-remote/files/289424c44e44db907abcaaa7-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadscedbabcaaajpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>↑↑↑↑↑↑↑↑↑↑ 我本身喜欢日漫，啊拉拉~~ ↑↑↑↑↑↑↑↑↑↑</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"/static-remote/files/fb542b6dd5e0296d503e9599-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsfbbddedejpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> <img src=\"/static-remote/files/08c269f3f29bd7d99b446465-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadscffbddbjpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>估计没有人会学我这样折腾一个城市suv，没办法呀，它有它必须具备的功能，我有我的喜好，自己喜欢就好。</p>\n<p>好了，带着它去旅行吧！最后附上2021年视频，全程Gopro拍摄，祝大家新年快乐：）</p>\n<p>可以直接去我的B站空间看自己拍摄和制作的视频哈：<a href=\"https://space.bilibili.com/259043\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://space.bilibili.com/259043</a></p>\n","slug":"18b5524b5102124575bf3e18","prev":[{"ID":823333,"title":"玩生活「Jeep小改, 越开越爱」","excerpt":"假如说工作是那么的循环反复索然无趣，那何不来点生活小充电？自己是一个独行侠，除去工作时间，大半时间都在各种人烟稀少的户外，可谓“原始人”。朋友这么叫我也不是没有道理的：）把自己的四驱小JEEP做了一点小改...","slug":"ca72e518978f61337a5681c1","post_date":"2020-12-24 10:30:11","post_date_gmt":"2020-12-24 10:30:11","thumbnail":[],"thumbnail_mini":[],"thumbnail_retina":[]}],"next":[{"ID":843333,"title":"使用React从零完整构建一个不错的网站「PoemKit的诞生」","excerpt":"沉醉于Web开发，我认为是一件富有诗意和美好的事情。我们可以用各种优秀的前端技术、UI组件和无限的可能性来点缀我们的想法。天马行空，总有我想做，我能做，我不能做的。 在这些过程中，很容易忘记我们为什么坚持这样做，以及一个不错的漂亮的的网站究竟是什么？","slug":"c9b2efad300f04dec769c6b8","post_date":"2021-11-12 17:07:09","post_date_gmt":"2021-11-12 17:07:09","thumbnail":["/static-remote/files/c945-com_146063ac038bbbd804602bea-770x340-4-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomacbbbdbeaxjpg.jpg",770,340,false],"thumbnail_mini":["/static-remote/files/c945-com_146063ac038bbbd804602bea-770x340-4-150x150-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomacbbbdbeaxxjpg.jpg",150,150,true],"thumbnail_retina":["/static-remote/files/c945-com_146063ac038bbbd804602bea-770x340-4-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomacbbbdbeaxjpg.jpg",770,340,false]}],"post_date":"2021-02-19 14:46:42","post_date_gmt":"2021-02-19 14:46:42","post_status":"publish","comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","post_password":"","to_ping":"","pinged":"","post_modified":"2022-11-17 02:12:50","post_modified_gmt":"2022-11-17 02:12:50","post_content_filtered":"","post_parent":0,"guid":"https://matrixflip.com/api/?post_type=post&#038;p=833333","menu_order":0,"post_type":"post","post_mime_type":"","comment_count":"0","filter":"raw"},"postID":"18b5524b5102124575bf3e18"},"__N_SSG":true}